=Bio=

"About to build the Self Supporting Village Sweden, a project which aims to create a self supporting village in rural mid Sweden. The biggest obstacle in mid Sweden is probably the cold and sun-empty climate during the winters, so housing will be the initial key part. If the village becomes successful, it can be used as a template for other villages.

All construction information will be licensed under some kind of open source license.

Contact info: mp underscore eriksson at yahoo dot se "


